  "title": "【黑白无双｜涂鸦log】房星",
  "summary": "含有少许黑白世界观oc，请继续看看我的倒霉cp😝",
  "content": "<p>含有少许黑白世界观oc，请继续看看我的倒霉cp<img src=\"https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/mu-plugins/wpcom-smileys/twemoji/2/72x72/1f61d.png\" alt=\"😝\"></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>钩吴与宛渠销赃中</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"791\" height=\"1023\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-1.png?w=791\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>白无常抢夺玉律</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"576\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-3.png?w=576\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>大家都很不幸，但鄱阳格外倒霉</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-4.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>一桩事先张扬的凶杀案（马尔克斯请见谅）</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-5.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>鹅鹅仔，你又在唐传奇啦！休息一下好不好</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-6.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>世界线变动，50%阴帅都是厉鬼</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"576\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-7.png?w=576\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>你们也是原教旨主义黑白无常</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-8.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>偶然想到：若木到咸阳城去，应该抛弃了自己的琴。是怀着怎样的心情抛弃的？说不定轻松地哼着歌，裁断了琴弦。</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-9.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>石轧铜杯（其一）</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"614\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-10.png?w=614\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>鄱阳困惑而凶险</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-11.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>石轧铜杯（其二）</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"682\" height=\"1023\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-12.png?w=682\" alt=\"in\"><figcaption>沉石与火舌（特朗斯特罗姆请见谅）</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"512\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-13.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>辞乡剑</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"812\" height=\"1023\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-14.png?w=812\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>酷吏</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"761\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-15.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>符节</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"692\" height=\"1023\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-16.png?w=692\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>残余下来的物质</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-17.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>我也试试画雪山<img src=\"https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/mu-plugins/wpcom-smileys/twemoji/2/72x72/1f4aa.png\" alt=\"💪\">（用的是揉餐巾纸的方法）</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"790\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-18.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>百鬼若木会露出一些生前没有的表情，很好味</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"789\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-19.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"796\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-20.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"602\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-21.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>您的道路行不通咗！</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/e69caae591bde5908de4bd9ce59381-1.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>惑星</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_9683.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>明亮之物</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_9732.jpeg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>平等掠夺</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_9952.jpeg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>山峦上的犬影（简坎皮恩请见谅）</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-22.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>曹雪钦补写大纲：<br>第二世若木在所出身的村庄，和钟馗原本是好友。<br>两人被分离后经历了截然不同的人生，三年后，在地府方面对蚩尤的正式战役前，于故乡重逢。</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-23.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>彼黍离离，彼稷之苗</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"619\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_0085.jpeg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"619\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_0086.jpeg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"619\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_0113.jpeg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"619\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_0117.jpeg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"932\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image.jpg?w=932\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>陟升皇之赫戏兮，忽临睨夫旧乡</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"671\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-24.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>跽俑</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-25.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"><figcaption>另一则唐传奇，天宝年间的蝴蝶幻戏团，牧蝶萨满故事主线^ ^</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"576\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-26.png?w=576\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"849\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-27.png?w=849\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://captainsang.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-28.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>",
